{
  "stem": "11998.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Except-- so there were only six-- six grades.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "After the sixth grade, like my sister went to gymnasium, and then that was already a Polish school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's where difficulties arose, because now she had non-Jewish teachers, and there was discrimination.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she always complained that her marks weren't given to her as she deserved because of this teacher or that teacher.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So these stories became very-- very troublesome to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Even as a child, as they became-- they were troublesome to the whole family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was, at the time of the war in 1939, I finished grade four.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my father was on the road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was selling merchandise to farmers and people in the mining communities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we lived a very simple life, as Jews live in all over the world.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was 8 [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a street not far from a beautiful park where we spent a lot of time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a mining town, so the most of my neighbors were children of miners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was only one Jewish family that lived-- was a tailor, who was very religious.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And who he was the one that went to the [NON-ENGLISH], whereas we went to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which was an orthodox synagogue, but it was like what we call here, a modern orthodox synagogue.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, the first thing that the Nazis did is they burned the synagogue down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The school is still standing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went to see it after the war, just a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, as a matter of fact, I took my family, just this year, back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
